[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":127},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F":109,"related:\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F":118},"\u002Fen\u002Fdocker\u002F2023\u002F01\u002F29\u002Fstep-by-step-docker-gui\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":93,"date":94,"description":18,"extension":95,"lang":96,"meta":97,"navigation":98,"path":99,"readingMinutes":100,"seo":101,"standalone":102,"stem":103,"tags":104,"tldr":106,"updated":94,"url":107,"__hash__":108},"content\u002F一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F10-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-Docker-GUI.md","(10)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - Docker GUI","345996692",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":86},"minimark",[11,15,19,23,26,29,35,38,43,46,49,55,58,61,67,70,73,77,80,83],[12,13,14],"h2",{"id":14},"前言",[16,17,18],"p",{},"接下來我想回頭講一下一直沒提到的東西，也就是 Docker 的 GUI。",[12,20,22],{"id":21},"docker-gui","Docker GUI",[16,24,25],{},"其實我們安裝 Docker 的時候，就已經安裝了 Docker GUI，只是我們一直都沒有去使用它而已，因為我認為一開始如果就直接使用 Docker GUI 來操作 Docker 並不是一個好習慣，因為我們實戰開發上來講還是比較常見用指令，如果能熟悉指令的話，其實在使用 GUI 上也會比較事半功倍。",[16,27,28],{},"如果你是使用 Mac 的話，通常啟用後會在你工具列上看到 Docker 的圖示，點擊後就可以看到 Docker GUI 的畫面了。",[16,30,31],{},[32,33],"img",{"alt":22,"src":34},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FOIrPXW0.png",[16,36,37],{},"接著請點一下 Dashboard，這樣你就可以看到 Docker 的狀態了",[16,39,40],{},[32,41],{"alt":22,"src":42},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002Fr2PD6Hf.png",[16,44,45],{},"透過這個 GUI 介面你可以快速啟動、暫停、刪除 Container 等，當然也可以查看 Images 等等，可以說是一個很方便的工具。",[16,47,48],{},"那麼當你點了 Image 的時候",[16,50,51],{},[32,52],{"alt":53,"src":54},"Image","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FJkKpNWm.png",[16,56,57],{},"可以查看這個 Image 預計會做哪些事情，也就是這個 Image 的 Dockerfile。",[16,59,60],{},"你也可以透過這個 GUI 快速進入 Container 的互動終端機模式",[16,62,63],{},[32,64],{"alt":65,"src":66},"open in terminal","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002FblogImg\u002Fdocker\u002F%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5%E6%AD%A5%E6%8E%8C%E6%8F%A1%E5%9F%BA%E7%A4%8E-Docker\u002FfpHaWTF.png",[16,68,69],{},"可以說是非常的方便呢。",[16,71,72],{},"因此假設你已經熟悉了 Docker 基本指令的話，不仿考慮使用 Docker GUI 來操作 Docker，這樣可以讓你開發速度更事半功倍唷！",[12,74,76],{"id":75},"window-安裝-docker","Window 安裝 Docker",[16,78,79],{},"Window 作業系統如果要安裝 Docker 的話，要稍微注意一下一些東西，因為有些開發者的電腦是採用家用版的，因此如果你要安裝 Docker 的話，會需要一些設置與前置動作，也就是要開啟 Window 中的 hyper-v 功能，這樣才能正常安裝 Docker。",[16,81,82],{},"那麼什麼是 hyper-v 呢？簡單來講就是一個虛擬化的技術，可以讓你在一台電腦上同時執行多個作業系統，也就是虛擬化的技術。",[16,84,85],{},"因此 Window 開發者會比較需要注意這一點就是了，如果是 Mac 或是 Linux 的話，就沒有這個問題了。",{"title":87,"searchDepth":88,"depth":88,"links":89},"",2,[90,91,92],{"id":14,"depth":88,"text":14},{"id":21,"depth":88,"text":22},{"id":75,"depth":88,"text":76},"docker","2023-01-29 15:20:19","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fdocker\u002F10-docker-docker-gui","1",{"title":6,"description":18},false,"一步步掌握基礎 Docker\u002F10-一步步掌握基礎-Docker-Docker-GUI",[93,105,22],"一步步掌握基礎 Docker",null,"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F345996692\u002F","V7LQbFQW9sItmJoB8epZPrZr2AaqJ64caS0VnwhA57c",{"newer":110,"older":114},{"url":111,"title":112,"date":113},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F1926467390\u002F","(11)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 目錄","2023-01-29 15:22:19",{"url":115,"title":116,"date":117},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20230129\u002F2952136309\u002F","(9)一步步掌握基礎 Docker - 將封裝好的 Docker 推到 Docker Hub","2023-01-29 00:15:09",[119,124,125],{"url":120,"title":121,"date":122,"readingMinutes":123},"\u002Fdocker\u002F20241219\u002F2070727594\u002F","如何將 Vite+Vue 封裝到 Docker 並運行？","2024-12-19 16:36:18","3",{"url":111,"title":112,"date":113,"readingMinutes":100},{"url":115,"title":116,"date":117,"readingMinutes":126},"2",1784011691486]